discord-userlinks:
{{optional}}
Used for display of the user links. Parameters
* $1 - User page link
* $2 - {{msg-mw|discord-talk}}
* $3 - {{msg-mw|discord-contribs}}

discord-revisionlinks:
{{Optional}}
Used for display of revision links. Parameters
* $1 - {{msg-mw|discord-diff}}
* $2 - {{msg-mw|discord-minor}}
* $3 - {{msg-mw|discord-size}}

discord-size:
{{Optional}}
Used as the text for $3 in discord-revisionlinks. Parameters
* $1 - Calculated revision size diff

discord-blocktimeformat:
{{optional}}

The formatting used in the date() function for displaying the time a user is blocked for.

See also: https://www.php.net/manual/en/datetime.format.php

discord-timestampformat:
{{optional}}

The formatting used in the gmdate() function for displaying the time an event happened in UTC.

See also: https://www.php.net/manual/en/datetime.format.php
